title: Belly Dancing
description:
https://yuq.me/users/15/891/oOhdyMmJVf.jpg

 Join Amira Mor and her dance troupe as they share with you the joyful, creative, empowering women?s art of Belly Dancing for Enlightenment. This age old technique of toning the body will give you an amazing workout in the comfort of your own home. Your instructor is Amira Mor, known around the world for her unique dance style, which integrates jazz and traditional Middle Eastern movements. The step-by-step instruction will exercise your upper and lower body. Belly Dancing for Enlightenment is: A healthy, creative, pleasurable and soulful form of self-expression. An avenue to being comfortable and confident in your own body. The oldest feminine dance-art in the world. The opportunity to wear beautiful, dazzling costumes made of colorful silks, brocades, sequins, and jewels
